HEADWORD: Copperworm
<hw>Cop"per*worm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The teredo; -- so called because it injures the
bottoms of vessels, where not protected by copper.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>The ringworm.</def>⟦br⟧
